        <IsA>data:font</IsA>
        <Summary>A version of Charis SIL with tighter line spacing</Summary>
        <Description>The Charis SIL Compact fonts were derived from Charis SIL using SIL TypeTuner, by setting the “Line spacing” feature to “Tight”, and they cannot be TypeTuned again. They may exhibit some diacritics clipping on screen (but should print fine).</Description>
